description: A slight breeze stirs the silken-threads of a monstrous cobweb, which almost entirely hides the eastern wall.

A slight breeze stirs the silken-threads of a monstrous cobweb, which almost entirely hides the eastern wall.  From a niche directly above what serves as a dining table for the denizens, eerily red glowing eyes shine brightly.  Piles of shredded clothing, helmets and other items lie in the corner.
title: [Catacombs, Cavern]
